{title: Case Insensitive Tags}

{start_of_verse: Verse 1}
[G]<B>Uppercase bold</B> on this line
[C]<I>Uppercase italic</I> on this line
[D]<BOLD>Another way</BOLD> to write bold
{end_of_verse}

{start_of_verse: Verse 2}
[G]<b>Lowercase bold</b> for comparison
[C]<i>Lowercase italic</i> for comparison
[D]Mixed <B>upper</B> and <b>lower</b> on one [G]line
{end_of_verse}

{start_of_chorus}
[C]<B><I>Upper bold italic</I></B>
[G]<b><i>Lower bold italic</i></b>
[D]<B><i>Mixed case nesting</i></B>
[G]Plain text at the [C]end
{end_of_chorus}
